{
  "name": "GET_AddPermission",
  "description": "<p>Adds a statement to a topic's access control policy, granting access for the specified Amazon Web Services accounts to the specified actions.</p> <note> <p>To remove the ability to change topic permissions, you must deny permissions to the <code>AddPermission</code>, <code>RemovePermission</code>, and <code>SetTopicAttributes</code> actions in your IAM policy.</p> </note>",
